description: The Safekeeper Forensic Evidence Drying Cabinet has a leading Multiplex™ filtration system, Air Science's ductless technology and provides continuous air flow to dry forensic evidence and remove airborne Pathogens, particles, smoke, and odors from objects. Combined with professional design and structure, it provides convenience and protects the safety of personnel.
name: Safekeeper Benchtop Forensic Evidence Drying Cabinet
